summary: The moviepage1.html file contributes to the system by providing a user interface for displaying information about a specific movie, "Logan". It includes a poster image, a summary of the movie, a video trailer, and a rating box for users to rate the movie. This file introduces HTML elements and styling for the movie display, as well as logic for capturing user ratings and displaying them dynamically. Additionally, it includes navigation options in a hamburger menu for users to visit different pages of the system.
